Events.Notes:
What:
Featuring local wineries, Del Sur residents will get a chance to taste wine paired with delicious bites. Bottles will be available to purchase. Once you have tasted them all, head over to our bar to sip on a glass of your favorite.
Winery #1: Volcan Winery
Winery #2: Ramona Ranch Winery
Winery #3: Hungry Hawk Vineyards
Winery #4: BK Cellars Winery

Food:
Delicious bites served up from Perfect Every Time catering.

Attire:
Cocktail attire.

Note:
We love throwing these adult socials!  Please be responsible and be sure to have a sober ride home or plan on walking.  We want to ensure that everyone has a great time and gets home safe!

RSVP:
You must purchase a ticket to attend this event.  You are required to show your Del Sur ID Card at our welcome table in order to attend the event.  Even if you have purchased a ticket, if you do not have your ID card, we will refund your money and ask you to leave.  Only CSC residents are allowed to attend this event.

Guests:
Guests are not permitted at this event.
